[[ Usage: ]]

The window layout:
    +-Win-------------------------------------------+
    |                                               |
    |   +-Ax------------------------------------+   |
    |   |                   ____/\              |   |
    |   | _Plt_/\__    ____/      \       ______|   |
    |   |          \__/            \_____/      |   |
    |   +---------------------------------------+   |
    |                                               |
    |   +-Ax-------------+      +-Ax------------+   |
    |   | *Plt**  *      |      | _      |_     |   |
    |   |      *       * |      | |_    _||_  _ |   |
    |   |       *  *     |      |_Plt_|_||||__|_|   |
    |   +----------------+      +---------------+   |
    |                                               |
    +-----------------------------------------------+


